High-end resorts are aware of the power of adding nature to their landscape design because they know the positive energy that green, living elements can bring to a space. From tabletop pieces to large-scale outdoor displays, high-end resorts know their guests will feel the positive energy that biophilic, or plant-based artistry naturally generates.  Let’s explore some contemporary landscape design techniques that have brought the natural beauty of plants to high-end resorts.

